Text: RE KellerThanks Glad to hear your doing well call any time Brian Original Message From Stepenovitch Joe mailtoJoe NRONcom Sent Thursday August PM To Subject FW Keller Good Afternoon Brian How have you been Im doing great I never got a chance to thank you and your coworker for the coffee mug Also I wanted to thank you again for dinner that night I still cant believe they acted that way Anyway I should get my promo to Mgr at the end of the year so well need to stay in touch and I might be in HotLanta soon as well Well I think you talked to my friend Keller today and he wanted me to forward you his resume I hope you and set him up with something Gotta run have a good holiday weekend and Ill talk to you soon Joe Step Jr Original Message From c starnes ENRON mailtoIMCEANOTEScstarnesCcstarnesyahooEcomEEN NRONcom Sent Friday August PM To Stepenovitch Joe Subject Keller Do You Yahoo Make international calls for as low as minute with Yahoo Messenger mswdoc mswdoc This email is the property of Enron Corp andor its relevant affiliate and may contain confidential and privileged material for the sole use of the intended recipient s Any review use distribution or disclosure by others is strictly prohibited If you are not the intended recipient or authorized to receive for the recipient please contact the sender or reply to Enron Corp at and delete all copies of the message This email and any attachments hereto are not intended to be an offer or an acceptance and do not create or evidence a binding and enforceable contract between Enron Corp or any of its affiliates and the intended recipient or any other party and may not be relied on by anyone as the basis of a contract by estoppel or otherwise Thank you winmaildat
